{"title":"我的工作无限光荣","authors":["多勷"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的工作无限光荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佳木斯工务段工人　多勷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个溜道工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的助手是旗灯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天摇旗接送车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜间溜道用色灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有武器道锤、道尺、螺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丝把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＠炖、炬火、信号是我的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防奸防特防事故，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注意钢轨和道钉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轨距线路上有障碍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的精神更集中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在桥梁、涵洞上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有建筑的地方我看清；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡到弯道、马道口、跟山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有爬行地点用目细眝盯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前后左右下侧面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我操心查分明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春季冰雪化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱草堆堆生；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"线路情况容易变化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把防汛工作先完成；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除了杂草侧沟清一清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏季“炎炎节”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上汗直淋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防备钢轨热涨病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕太阳晒，蚊虫咬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我同样来回巡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋季雨水多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和水害作斗争；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雨淋透背脊心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水淹住下半身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢救工作我一刻也不停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬季大雪纷纷下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕天寒地冻冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着北风来扫雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻害消灭不发生；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的任务来完成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个溜道工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的生命财产由我负责"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加强巡回来溜道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭事故防敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证列车运转得安宁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个溜道工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个溜道工；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的任务非常重大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的工作无限光荣！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}